    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "坐在桌子对面，冲我撒娇的女孩。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "初次见面时，看着简单普通，但却蕴藏着某种力量的女孩。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "以及此刻，隔着黑夜，站在我对面的女孩。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "而回想这些只用了一瞬间，却又像是过了好多年。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我喜欢——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "刚要说话，嘴唇便被苔丝的食指堵住了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
